{"tid":2156940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗蘋果之外，仲有一間媒體好需要大家支持","createTime":"2020-08-14T19:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T09:45:22.000Z","uid":226913,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"844322fa00744fc054ddca43ae8cfd15c6f79d54","tid":2156940,"uid":226913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T19:39:09.000Z","msg":"呢間就係白羅斯第一間獨立電視台 - Belsat <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j1znBKW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj1znBKW.png&h=f992b9ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚴格來講 Belsat 係一間波蘭經營既電視台，但係佢地既廣播對象主要係白羅斯人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十幾年前，佢地開始批評白羅斯政府，換來既後果當然就係比當地政府不斷打壓。雖然係咁，依然有唔少白羅斯人睇到佢地既報導，今次示威佢地亦扮演非常重要既角色，好多一手消息都係由佢地報導 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔識俄文可以follow佢地英文twitter:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Belsat_Eng\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBelsat_Eng&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=f4646bba\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Belsat_Eng</a><br />\nLive直播:<br />\n<a href=\"https://belsat.eu/online/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbelsat.eu%2Fonline%2F&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=ee4d0554\" target=\"_blank\">https://belsat.eu/online/</a><br />\nFacebook:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BELSAT.TV/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBELSAT.TV%2F&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=8d252294\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BELSAT.TV/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記，白羅斯政府係其中一個支持國安法既國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推翻極權暴政，人人有責！"},{"pid":"76328de58b2c0e36f7ddd5912c6b3c16c5f13406","tid":2156940,"uid":226913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T19:42:09.000Z","m